# Exclude JSON data files from GitHub's language statistics
*.json linguist-vendored

# Exclude markdown docs from language statistics (optional, but keeps focus on code)
*.md linguist-vendored

# Exclude SVG icons/images from language statistics
*.svg linguist-vendored

# Explicitly mark frontend code so it is counted properly
*.js linguist-detectable
*.jsx linguist-detectable
*.css linguist-detectable
*.html linguist-detectable

# Explicitly mark backend code
*.py linguist-detectable
